body_html:
@alanchiao , As of now we don't have any speech models which are in LSTM Quant and available in TFLite, I assume some of the below tflite models may be quant lstm model and we like to run this model as part of TFLite Speech apk and run its full network to understand further.
speech_hotword_model_rank1_2017_11_14.tflite
speech_speakerid_model_2017_11_14.tflite
speech_tts_model_2017_11_14.tflite
speech_hotword_model_rank2_2017_11_14.tflite
speech_terse_am_model_2017_11_14.tflite

My goal is to run speech Quant model(lstm quant) on TFLite running on ubuntu and as well on Android.

if possible could you please generate these models in order to run with the latest TensorFlowlite code and update it.
